Mademoiselle de Soissons (1665–1705) AKA Princess Marie Jeanne of Savo...

This portrait is identified as being Princess Jeanne of Savoy (1665–1705). She was the daughter of Prince Eugene Maurice of Savoy, Count of Soissons and Dreux (1635–1673) and Olimpia Mancini (1640–1708).
